Invocation Name: beef dairy network
des:
Welcome to the Beef and Dairy Network Alexa Skill, the Alexa companion to the Beef and Dairy Network podcast and website.

Have you ever been in the milking parlour and suddenly wanted to know the plural of beef, but didn't have any hands free so you couldn't check your phone? Then this skill's for you.

The Beef and Dairy Network Alexa Skill is brought to you by network member Alasdair Nicol. All bovine content is from Benjamin Partridge and the contributors of the podcast.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
